00:31:47,500 --> 00:31:48,780
 even though I don't feel like it right now.

647
00:31:48,780 --> 00:31:50,660
 Jesus, you know, give me grace.

648
00:31:50,660 --> 00:31:52,540
 Jesus, forgive me for my attitude, blah, blah, blah.

